<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Codeforces - Tag | SPAWN2PWN</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/tags/codeforces/</link><description>Hugo FixIt 作者，喜欢瞎折腾、造轮子、写东西，分享一些前端开发中的所见、所闻、所思。</description><generator>Hugo 0.163.3 &amp; FixIt v0.4.5</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</managingEditor><webMaster>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</webMaster><copyright>This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 18:39:48 +0700</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/tags/codeforces/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Dreamoon and Stairs</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/codeforces476a/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Aug 2018 20:13:08 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/codeforces476a/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://codeforces.com/contest/476/problem/a" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;题目链接&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dreamoon wants to climb up a stair of n steps. He can climb 1 or 2 steps at each move. Dreamoon wants the number of moves to be a multiple of an integer m.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What is the minimal number of moves making him climb to the top of the stairs that satisfies his condition?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="input"&gt;&lt;span&gt;10 Input&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#input" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The single line contains two space separated integers n, m (0 &amp;lt; n ≤ 10000, 1 &amp;lt; m ≤ 10).&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dreamoon and WiFi（组合数学）</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/codeforces476b/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Aug 2018 17:44:47 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/codeforces476b/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://codeforces.com/contest/476/problem/B" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;题目链接&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="题目大意"&gt;&lt;span&gt;10 题目大意&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e9%a2%98%e7%9b%ae%e5%a4%a7%e6%84%8f" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;就是给定两个字符串，第一个字符串由&amp;quot;+&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;-&amp;ldquo;组成，第二个字符串由&amp;rdquo;+&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;-&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;?&amp;ldquo;组成，“+”代表加 1，&amp;rdquo;-&amp;ldquo;代表减一，“?&amp;ldquo;代表可取正也可取负，问第二个字符串的位置和第一个字符串相等的概率是多少。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我一开始的想法是把（+1，-1）^n 看成和二项式定理一样的展开始式，只不过把乘法改为加法，然后得到公式&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;c(n,0)(n+(-1)0)+c(n,1)(n-1+(-1)1)+c(n,i)(n-i+(-1)i)+...+c(n,n)(n-n+(-1)n)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
化简一下可知通项为&lt;code&gt;c(n,i)(n-2*i)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
然后我对第一个串求出位置 sum, 第二个串先求出已知位置 sum1，然后记录下？的个数，然后遍历找出展开式中某一项 n-2i+sum1==sum，这样 x 的系数就是可能出现位置相等的所有情况，用 (n-2i)/系数和就是概率了啊，可是为什么不对呢，本地调试，数据没问题，可是交到 cf 上第二组都过不了，烦亏我还觉得想到一个独辟的方法呢，过不了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;//cf 错误报告，思前恐后不晓得 why,wtf??? 先码着吧
Test: #2, time: 0 ms., memory: 0 KB, exit code: 0, checker exit code: 1, verdict: WRONG_ANSWER
Input
&amp;#43;-&amp;#43;-
&amp;#43;-??
Output
-0.000000000000
Answer
0.500000000000
Checker Log
wrong answer 1st numbers differ - expected: &amp;#39;0.5000000&amp;#39;, found: &amp;#39;-0.0000000&amp;#39;, error = &amp;#39;0.5000000&amp;#39;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="错误代码"&gt;&lt;span&gt;11 错误代码&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e9%94%99%e8%af%af%e4%bb%a3%e7%a0%81" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;#include&amp;lt;bits/stdc&amp;#43;&amp;#43;.h&amp;gt;
using namespace std;

int main(){
 int i,j,cnt=0;
 long long c[11][11],sum=0,sum1=0;
 for(i = 0; i &amp;lt; 11; i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;){//杨辉三角
 c[i][0] = 1;
 c[i][i] = 1;
 for(j = 1; j &amp;lt; i; j&amp;#43;&amp;#43;)
 c[i][j] = c[i-1][j] &amp;#43; c[i-1][j-1];
 }
 string a,b;
 cin&amp;gt;&amp;gt;a&amp;gt;&amp;gt;b;
 //cout&amp;lt;&amp;lt;a&amp;lt;&amp;lt;endl&amp;lt;&amp;lt;b&amp;lt;&amp;lt;endl;
 int len=a.length();
 for(i=0;i&amp;lt;len;i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;)
 if(a[i]==&amp;#39;&amp;#43;&amp;#39;) sum&amp;#43;=1;
 else sum-=1;
 for(i=0;i&amp;lt;b.length();i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;){
 if(b[i]==&amp;#39;&amp;#43;&amp;#39;) sum1&amp;#43;=1;
 else if(b[i]==&amp;#39;-&amp;#39;)sum1-=1;
 if(b[i]==&amp;#39;?&amp;#39;) cnt&amp;#43;&amp;#43;;
 }
 if(sum==sum1&amp;amp;&amp;amp;cnt==0){
 printf(&amp;#34;1.000000000000\n&amp;#34;);
 return 0;
 }
 int flag=0;
 int x=0;
 for(j=0;j&amp;lt;=cnt;j&amp;#43;&amp;#43;)
 x&amp;#43;=c[cnt][j];
 //cout&amp;lt;&amp;lt;x&amp;lt;&amp;lt;endl;
 for(i=0;i&amp;lt;=cnt;i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;)
 if(cnt-2*i&amp;#43;sum1==sum){
 flag=1;
 long double y=c[cnt][i]*1.0/x;
 printf(&amp;#34;%.12llf\n&amp;#34;,y);
 }
 if(!flag)printf(&amp;#34;0.000000000000\n&amp;#34;);
 return 0;
}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;想不通，没办法只好换思路。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Codeforces Round 502(Div.1 + Div.2)</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/cfcontest1017/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 Aug 2018 10:48:00 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/cfcontest1017/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;h3 class="heading-element" id="a-the-rank"&gt;&lt;span&gt;0.7 &lt;a href="https://codeforces.com/contest/1017/problem/A" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;A. The Rank&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#a-the-rank" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;题目大意：&lt;br&gt;
给出 n 个学生的成绩，Thomas Smith 的成绩是第一行，然后要按总成绩进行排序，总分相同的按编号从小到大排；&lt;br&gt;
开始看还以为要写 sort 的 cmp 函数进行多条件排序，敲完才发现其实只要按总分就可以了，因为托马斯的 id 是一，必然会排在前面。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Bear and Finding Criminals-Codeforces680B</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/codeforces680b/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 Jul 2018 19:32:21 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/codeforces680b/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;p&gt;题目链接：&lt;a href="https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/680/B" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;Bear and Finding Criminals&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;大致题意就是小熊警察住在某个城市，他要抓各个城市的罪犯，现在用一个 BCD 可以知道那个城市里&lt;strong&gt;一定&lt;/strong&gt;有罪犯。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一定能确定该城市有小偷的几种情况：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;警察所住城市有罪犯，则一定能检测到&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;警察所住城市的左边和右边位置若&lt;strong&gt;都&lt;/strong&gt;不为 0，则说明两座城市都有罪犯（只有一边为 1 是不能确定到底哪个城市有罪犯的）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;警察所在城市的一边检测到有罪犯，但在另一边已经没有城市了，则说明该城市一定有罪犯&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</description></item><item><title>Bear and Five Cards-Codeforces680A</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/codeforces680a/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 Jul 2018 19:22:36 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/codeforces680a/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;p&gt;题目链接：&lt;a href="https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/680/A" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;Bear and Five Cards&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;大致题意就是小熊有 5 张卡片，每张卡片有对应的分数，他可以选择丢弃 2 张相同的或者 3 张相同的卡片，没有相同的就无法丢弃，问小熊剩下的分数最少是多少。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Piles-with-stones</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/piles-with-stones/</link><pubDate>Tue, 31 Jul 2018 11:09:31 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/piles-with-stones/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;p&gt;Codeforces Round #500 (Div. 2)&lt;br&gt;
题目链接：&lt;a href="https://codeforces.com/contest/1013/problem/A" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;Piles With Stones&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Adjacent Replacements</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/adjacent-replacements/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Jul 2018 11:54:14 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/adjacent-replacements/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://codeforces.com/contest/1006/problem/A" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;A. Adjacent Replacements&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;第一次打 cf 就做出一道这样的找规律的题，打到自闭。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;#include&amp;lt;bits/stdc&amp;#43;&amp;#43;.h&amp;gt;
using namespace std;

int main(){
 int n,a[1001];
 cin&amp;gt;&amp;gt;n;
 int i;
 int flag=0;
 for(i=0;i&amp;lt;n;i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;){
 cin&amp;gt;&amp;gt;a[i];
 if(!(a[i]&amp;amp;1)) a[i]--;
 if(!flag) {cout&amp;lt;&amp;lt;a[i];flag=1;}
 else cout&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;#34; &amp;#34;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;a[i];
 }
 return 0;
}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description></item><item><title>Educational Codeforces Round 47 (Rated for Div. 2)</title><link>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/cf-1009/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Jul 2018 11:25:56 +0800</pubDate><author>1024@lruihao.cn (Lruihao)</author><guid>https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/cf-1009/</guid><category domain="https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/categories/acm/">ACM</category><description>&lt;p&gt;那天晚上报名了没打，第二天早上打的，也只出了两题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="a-game-shopping"&gt;&lt;span&gt;7 &lt;a href="https://codeforces.com/contest/1009/problem/A" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;A. Game Shopping&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#a-game-shopping" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;#include&amp;lt;iostream&amp;gt;
using namespace std;

int main(){
 int n,m,s=0;
 cin&amp;gt;&amp;gt;n&amp;gt;&amp;gt;m;
 int i,j;
 int c[1000],a[1000];
 for(i=0;i&amp;lt;n;i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;)
 cin&amp;gt;&amp;gt;c[i];
 for(i=0;i&amp;lt;m;i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;)
 cin&amp;gt;&amp;gt;a[i];
 for(i=0,j=0;i&amp;lt;n;){
 if(j==m)
 break;
 if(c[i]&amp;lt;=a[j]){
 s&amp;#43;&amp;#43;;
 j&amp;#43;&amp;#43;;
 i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;;
 }
 else i&amp;#43;&amp;#43;;
 }
 if(i==n&amp;amp;&amp;amp;s==0)
 cout&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;#34;0\n&amp;#34;;
 else cout&amp;lt;&amp;lt;s&amp;lt;&amp;lt;endl;
